videos.headline: Fields runs it in for 7-yard TD
videos.description: Justin Fields gets Ohio State on the board first with a 7-yard rushing touchdown in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fields runs it in for 7-yard TD) 2019/9/7

videos.headline: Dobbins runs it up the gut for the TD
videos.description: J.K. Dobbins gets the handoff and runs it right up the middle for a Buckeyes touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dobbins runs it up the gut for the TD) 2019/9/7

videos.headline: Dobbins takes off for 60-yard TD
videos.description: J.K. Dobbins finds an open hole and flies down the field en route to an Ohio State 60-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Fields finds Wilson for 9-yard TD
videos.description: Justin Fields finds Garrett Wilson for a 9-yard touchdown, Wilson's first touchdown as a Buckeye.
